Subject: [PATCH 4.14 078/237] media: v4l2-device.h: Explicitly compare grp{id,mask} to zero in v4l2_device macros
Date:   Thu, 27 Feb 2020 14:34:52 +0100
Message-Id: <20200227132302.857774937@linuxfoundation.org>
